Class CSPortalPolicyFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jalios.jcms.policy.AbstractPolicyFilter
      • com.jalios.jcms.policy.BasicPortalPolicyFilter
        • com.jalios.jcmsplugin.collaborativespace.CSPortalPolicyFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.jalios.jcms.plugin.PluginComponent, com.jalios.jcms.policy.PolicyFilter, com.jalios.jcms.policy.PortalPolicyFilter, CSConstants, java.lang.Comparable
    public class CSPortalPolicyFilter
extends com.jalios.jcms.policy.BasicPortalPolicyFilter
implements CSConstants
    This PolicyFilter has several purposes:
    • forces portal to stay in collaborative space presentation by typology portal, or to go the CS portal
    • forces a CSRequest to be displayed in its storage workspace
    Since:
    csp-3
    Author:
    Olivier Dedieu <olivier.dedieu@jalios.com>, Sylvain DEVAUX <sylvain.devaux@jalios.com>
